history.content:
Hi folks,


Phase two is underway so I'm here to remind you of a few resources available to help. Bookmark them!

EE Upper Division Showcase: A youtube channel of faculty discussing their Upper Division EE courses

HKN Course Map and Course Pages: https://hkn.eecs.berkeley.edu/courseguides

Info on Getting into CS Courses: https://eecs.berkeley.edu/resources/undergrads/cs/degree-reqs/enrollment-policy

Info on Getting into EE Courses: https://eecs.berkeley.edu/resources/undergrads/eecs/degree-reqs/enrollment-policy
